  Requirements:
    - php 4.1.0 or later
    - MySQL 3.23.32 or later
    - Krecipes MySQL database version 0.85 or later
    - a web-browser could be useful... ;-)


  Summary:
    Krecipes Web Frontend is intended to display the Krecipes MySQL database on the WWW.
    Currently it can:
      - Display the categories & recipes
      - Multilangual (curently only english & norwegian)
      - Got a print page for easing print layout (improved in 0.2b)
      - Full css implementation (improved in 0.2b)
      - 'Send to a friend' feature
      More will come...



  Download:
    You can get the newest version at http://krecipesweb.berlios.de/.

